description.en:
LionIsland Inu has a purpose of creating an NFT private island community for $LIONISLAND owners, every owners can receive a banner image NFT featuring their own unique, randomly generated private bungalows and populate our huge island and play freely.

The function of these NFT are to be used in our exclusive Lazy Lions Play-to-Earn game.

LionIsland Inu is a new revolutionary type of Play-to-Earn game.
